this is a config dir used by task.sync.gobo to synchronize machines.

layout.all				gobolinux root partition layout common to all machines.
layout.$profile				gobolinux root partition layout specific to a machine profile.
programs.current-version.all		common programs needed on all machines, taken from current version on this machine.
programs.current-version.$profile	additional programs needed by a certain machine profile, taken from current version on this machine.
programs.specific-version.$profile	additional programs especially compiled for a certain machine profile.


